data.value:
Our restaurant is located in the heart of the Old City next to the pearl of Baku – the “Maidens Tower“facing the Caspian Sea and the Boulevard. In other words, our location is extremely beneficial for any visitor hoping to easily access all that Museum Inn Boutique Hotel has to offer.
Dear guests we look forward to welcoming you at the “Museum Inn Boutique Hotel & Restaurant” in Baku,and assure you of our best personal attention at all times. Should you require any further information or need assistance, please contact us directly.
